# Function: ChangeDesk
#
# This function is called by FvwmEvent every time the Desk is changed.
DestroyFunc ChangeDesk
AddToFunc   ChangeDesk
+ I SendToModule FvwmButtons ChangeButton desk0 Colorset 10
+ I SendToModule FvwmButtons ChangeButton desk1 Colorset 10
+ I SendToModule FvwmButtons ChangeButton desk2 Colorset 10
+ I SendToModule FvwmButtons ChangeButton desk3 Colorset 10
+ I SendToModule FvwmButtons ChangeButton desk$0 Colorset 11

# FvwmEvent
#
# FvwmEvent is a module that can run an action or function
# on specific events. This instance changes which desk number
# is highlighted when the desk is changed.
DestroyModuleConfig EventNewDesk:*
*EventNewDesk: PassID
*EventNewDesk: new_desk ChangeDesk

# FvwmForm
#
# FvwmForm is a module that can be used to build a GUI
# form. Used with fvwm-menu-desktop-config.fpl.
# This sets the default colorsets.
*FvwmFormDefault: Colorset 10
*FvwmFormDefault: ItemColorset 13

# redefine to not warp the cursor
DestroyFunc WindowListFunc
AddToFunc WindowListFunc
+ I Iconify off
+ I FlipFocus
+ I Raise

##################################################################################
# AutoHide                                                                       #
# http://www.fvwm.org/documentation/faq/#autohiding-fvwmbuttons-or-other-windows #
##################################################################################

*FvwmEvent: add_window AutoHidePlacementHandler

DestroyFunc AutoHide
AddToFunc AutoHide
	+ I ThisWindow ($0) Deschedule $[w.id]
	+ I ThisWindow ($0) KeepRc ThisWindow (shaded) WindowShade off
	+ I TestRc (!Match) All ($0, !shaded) AutoHideHide $1 $2

DestroyFunc AutoHideHide
AddToFunc AutoHideHide
	+ I Schedule $0 $[w.id] WindowShade $1
	+ I Schedule $0 $[w.id] Deschedule $[w.id]

DestroyFunc AutoHideEnter
AddToFunc AutoHideEnter

DestroyFunc AutoHidePlacementHandler
AddToFunc AutoHidePlacementHandler

AddToFunc AutoHideEnter
	+ I AutoHide TopPanel 500 N
	+ I AutoHide xclock 500 E
	+ I AutoHide xload 500 E
	+ I AutoHide log 500 S
	+ I AutoHide clock.FvwmScript 500 S

AddToFunc AutoHidePlacementHandler
	+ I Schedule 1000 ThisWindow ("xclock") WindowShade E
	+ I Schedule 1000 ThisWindow ("xload") WindowShade E
	+ I Schedule 1000 ThisWindow ("log") WindowShade S
	+ I Schedule 1000 ThisWindow ("clock.FvwmScript") WindowShade S

Style "clock.FvwmScript" !Title, Sticky, NeverFocus, WindowListSkip, WindowShadeSteps $[infostore.auto_hide_steps], WindowShadeScrolls, WindowShadeBusy, !Borders, StaysOnBottom
Style "log" !Title, Sticky, NeverFocus, WindowListSkip, WindowShadeSteps $[infostore.auto_hide_steps], WindowShadeScrolls, WindowShadeBusy
Style "xclock" !Title, Sticky, NeverFocus, WindowListSkip, WindowShadeSteps $[infostore.auto_hide_steps], WindowShadeScrolls, WindowShadeBusy
Style "xload" !Title, Sticky, NeverFocus, WindowListSkip, WindowShadeSteps $[infostore.auto_hide_steps], WindowShadeScrolls, WindowShadeBusy

DestroyModuleConfig FvwmAuto: *

AddToFunc StartFunction
	+ I Module FvwmAuto 0 -menter AutoHideEnter